body.head:
256. Telegram From the Department of State to the Embassy in MoroccoSource: National Archives, RG 59,
                    Central Foreign Policy File, D800365–0950. Secret; Immediate; Exdis. Sent for information Immediate to
                    Algiers. Drafted by Coon;
                    cleared in NEA, INR/RNA, S/P, NSC, P, PM, and L;
                    approved by Christopher.
